sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Desired as Desired state
  participant Authority
  participant StemA as Stem owner epoch N
  participant Cell
  participant Chamber
  participant StemB as Successor epoch N+1

  Desired->>Authority: request replica increase
  StemA->>Authority: read canonical snapshot under lease N
  StemA->>Authority: commit deterministic plan and exact actions
  Authority-->>Cell: fenced action for current Cell generation
  Cell->>Chamber: converge successor residency
  Chamber-->>Cell: ready only after runtime and custody agree
  Cell-->>Authority: signed current observation
  Note over Authority,StemA: Process liveness is not readiness. Authority and observation must agree.
  StemA--xAuthority: owner lost before next reconciliation
  Authority->>StemB: grant lease epoch N+1 after expiry and takeover evidence
  StemB->>Authority: read current snapshot and prior outcomes
  StemB->>Authority: continue only unapplied current actions
  Authority-->>Cell: next exact action or stable no-op
  Cell-->>Authority: converged observation
